parameters.description:
Upload date filter.
Available options:
l - last hour;
t - today;
w - weak ago;
m - month ago;
y - year ago;

Result sort. Available options:
r - relevance;
ra - rating;
u - upload date;
v - view count;

Video features.  Available options(could be joined by ';'):
h - hdr;
hd - hd;
s - subtitles;
c - cc;
3d - 3d;
3 - 360;
li - live;
lo - location;
4 - 4k;

Video duration. Available options:
s - short;
l - long;

Search type. Available options:
v - video;
c - channel;
p - playlist;
